CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier, November 5, 1955, pg. 1B reads: "Dr. Azikiwe and an old classmate, Clarence Holt, merchandising executive for B.B.D. & O., chat with Mrs. Robert L. Vann, president of The Courier."
TitMainTitle: Jessie Vann standing between Eastern Nigerian Prime Minister Nnamdi Azikiwe and Clarence Holt in office in Pittsburgh Courier
